<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetStandardOut.Create" Title="Create method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetStandardOut">LogTargetStandardOut</PageRef> ->
    Create
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>Create</TypeRef> method creates a standard output target and returns it wrapped in a smart pointer compatible with <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.AddLogTarget">LogManager.AddLogTarget</PageRef>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[static std::unique_ptr<LogTargetStandardOut, ILogTarget::Deleter> Create(bool flushAfterOutput);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="bool" Name="flushAfterOutput">If <TypeRef>true</TypeRef>, the target flushes <TypeRef>std::cout</TypeRef> after every message.</ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="LogTargetStandardOut!cobalt.logging.LogTargetStandardOut">
        A newly constructed <TypeRef>LogTargetStandardOut</TypeRef> object wrapped in a smart pointer that uses <TypeRef>ILogTarget::Deleter</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetStandardOut">LogTargetStandardOut</PageRefListEntry>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.AddLogTarget">LogManager.AddLogTarget</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
